1.Question 1
The algorithm for consensus in the Bitcoin blockchain is called _____ protocol.


Proof of Stake


Proof of Work  -------correct


Proof of Worth


Proof of Elapsed Time

Correct
Correct! It gets its name because it involves “work” or computational power to solve the puzzle and to claim the right to form the next block.

