2.Question 2
Transaction confirmation is independently performed by all miner nodes. True or False?


False


True    -------correct

Correct
Correct! Miners, take on added work or computation to verify transactions, broadcast transactions, compete to claim the right to create a block, work on reaching consensus by validating the block, broadcasting the newly created block and confirming transactions.

1 / 1 point
